Bille Incendiaire !

00:10:51.180 --> 00:10:54.520
Misère !
Bille Incendiaire ! Bille Incendiaire !

00:10:55.060 --> 00:10:57.120
Bille Incendiaire ! Bille Incendiaire !

00:11:00.120 --> 00:11:01.150
Usopp !

00:11:03.280 --> 00:11:05.250
Tire-toi ! Tire-toi !

00:11:14.970 --> 00:11:16.290
Usopp !

00:11:23.670 --> 00:11:24.520
Sanji.

00:11:27.020 --> 00:11:28.480
Purée !

00:11:30.560 --> 00:11:31.930
Arrête, Sanji !

00:11:41.650 --> 00:11:42.690
