00:13:25.670 --> 00:13:27.640
Strong Right !

00:13:29.890 --> 00:13:30.600
Quoi ?

00:13:34.730 --> 00:13:36.860
Attends !
Ne fais pas ça, Luffy !

00:13:37.360 --> 00:13:38.930
