00:13:39.180 --> 00:13:40.640
Jet Pistol !

00:13:53.960 --> 00:13:54.910
Luffy !

00:13:58.000 --> 00:13:59.380
Non !

00:14:07.550 --> 00:14:09.140
Luffy ! Au sec...

00:14:10.600 --> 00:14:12.270
Nami !

00:14:48.890 --> 00:14:50.470
Luffy ! Au sec...

